Client Code *: At least one of Client Code OR Client Name is required; Max 20 chars
Client Name *: At least one of Client Code OR Client Name is required; Max 200 chars
State *: Mandatory Field; Must be a valid state from Client's Country
Latitude: non mandatory; Must be a valid Latitude value
Longitude: non mandatory; Must be a valid Longitude value
Field A: If you need to import data for custom fields specify the name of custom field in column header. Remove column if there are no custom fields.
Field B: If you need to import data for custom fields specify the name of custom field in column header. Remove column if there are no custom fields.
